:INFO
Live-Aboard Remote Work Gear
Essential equipment for a productive and resilient work setup on a sailing vessel.

:TASK
[ ] Starlink Roam or Maritime terminal and mount
[ ] 12V to USB-C laptop charging cable
[ ] Waterproof pelican case for electronics
[ ] Travel router with cellular failover
[ ] Portable solar panel for cockpit charging
[ ] Waterproof bluetooth keyboard
[ ] Noise-cancelling headphones with long battery life
[ ] Starlink flat mount or rail mount adapter
[ ] Shore power inlet adapter for marina hookup

:NOTE
Corrosion is the enemy of boat electronics. Use marine-grade connectors, apply contact cleaner regularly, and store gear in sealed bins when underway.

:LINK
https://www.starlink.com/roam
Starlink Roam: Mobile Satellite Internet
